{"title":"田头估产记","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"田头估产记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻王清晨起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开眼吃一惊；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何来许多人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田塍闹盈盈；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一亩八千五，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一亩一万零。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争来又争去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难把产量定。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干部经验少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去把专家请；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书上查不出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急得脸通红；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再去搬救兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请来老农民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老农看又想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两眼直发楞；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖辈种水稻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁见这光景："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻丛密又壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻头尺多长；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一穗靠一穗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风来吹不动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盘算老半天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是算不清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐去问稻王，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻王笑脸迎："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争取上北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的儿孙辈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"空前大繁荣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"究竟有多少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也蒙懂懂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但等黄熟后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收下称一称；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农学重新写，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编本“跃进经”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚稻超早稻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金榜题大名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载浙江日报）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}